<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Section Number="0744.357" xmlns="http://StatRev.xsd"><Catchline xml:space="preserve">Liability of surety.</Catchline><SectionBody><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">No surety for a guardian shall be charged beyond the property of the ward.</Text></SectionBody><History xml:space="preserve">s. 1, ch. 74-106; ss. 19, 26, ch. 75-222; s. 43, ch. 89-96; s. 27, ch. 90-271.</History><Note><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">Created from former s. 744.43.</Text></Note></Section>